{"word":"G2154 - εὔσημος - eúsēmos - yoo'-say-mos - Easy to be understood","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὔσημος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eúsēmos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo'-say-mos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Easy to be understood</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தெளிவான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"well - marked, clear and definite, distinct"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G4591 - σημαίνω - sēmaínō - say-mah'-ee-no/4591\">G4591</a>; <i>well indicated</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>significant:</i> - easy to be understood.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1978/1978\">G1978</a>, <a href=\"#/G2154/2154\">G2154</a>, <a href=\"#/G4591/4591\">G4591</a>, <a href=\"#/G4592/4592\">G4592</a>, <a href=\"#/G4593/4593\">G4593</a>, <a href=\"#/G4953/4953\">G4953</a>, <a href=\"#/G767/767\">G767</a>"}]}